## ⚙️ Configuration

### Environment Variables

The `.env` file contains all environment-specific settings. Key variables:

```env
APP_NAME=EdoOdyssey
APP_ENV=local
APP_DEBUG=true
APP_URL=http://localhost:8000

DB_CONNECTION=mysql          # or sqlite
DB_HOST=127.0.0.1
DB_PORT=3306
DB_DATABASE=edoodyssey
DB_USERNAME=root
DB_PASSWORD=secret

SESSION_DRIVER=file
CACHE_STORE=file
```

### CMS Settings

Administrators can manage site-wide settings via the **Admin > CMS Settings** panel:
- Site Name
- Contact Phone / Email / Address
- About EDSTA (footer description)
- Footer Text
- Meta Description (SEO)

