## 🗄️ Database Setup

### SQLite (Default for Local)

```bash
touch database/database.sqlite
```
Then set `DB_CONNECTION=sqlite` in `.env`.

### MySQL (Production)

Set the following in `.env`:

```env
DB_CONNECTION=mysql
DB_HOST=127.0.0.1
DB_PORT=3306
DB_DATABASE=edoodyssey
DB_USERNAME=root
DB_PASSWORD=yourpassword
```

Run migrations:

```bash
php artisan migrate --seed
```

