## 🧪 Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

| Issue | Solution |
|-------|----------|
| `The only supported ciphers are AES-128-CBC and AES-256-CBC` | Generate a new app key: `php artisan key:generate` |
| `SQLSTATE[HY000] [2002] No such file or directory` | SQLite path issue – set `DB_DATABASE` to absolute path or use MySQL. |
| `Class 'App\Models\QrCode' not found` | Run `composer dump-autoload` and clear caches. |
| `403 Forbidden` on admin | Ensure the user has `is_admin = 1` or correct role. |
| `404 Not Found` on routes | Run `php artisan route:clear` and `php artisan route:cache`. |

### Cache Clearing

```bash
php artisan optimize:clear
php artisan config:clear
php artisan view:clear
php artisan route:clear
php artisan cache:clear
```

